name: Anaerobic Capacity Maintenance #1
description:
The focus today is on quality. With this in mind, the intensity is completed early in the session with 8 x 1 Min Anaerobic Capacity Intervals, before finishing with a 25 Min zone 2 effort. Observe your Heart Rate response during the 25 Min effort. How much does it increase throughout the effort?
